In order for you to add voice notes on lead or in post call disposition screen, or to send voice messages Salesmax needs record audio permission.

Allow Salesmax to make phone calls. This permission enables you to make direct calls from within the app. By allowing this permission, you can seamlessly integrate call functions, ensuring that all your business interactions are efficiently logged and managed.

Salesmax needs access to your call logs to automatically track and log your business calls. This helps you manage your client interactions, analyze call data, and maintain accurate records of your communications.It Also needs Permission to be able to send you notifications such as task reminders.

Allow Salesmax to access your contacts to import selected contacts as leads. This will enable you to call, send WhatsApp messages, follow up, record outcomes, and more, directly from the app.
Allow Salesmax to access your contacts to get smart actionable features to your contacts.

Allow Salesmax to draw over other apps. This permission enables features such as displaying the context of each incoming or outgoing call from your business contacts and prompting you to log call outcomes
